<template>
  <v-container class="lighten-5">
    <v-row no-gutters>
      <v-col md="4">
        <v-card
          class="mx-auto"
          max-width="500"
          :mini-variant.sync="mini"
          mini-variant-width="80"
          width="260"
        >
          <template
            v-if="drawerImage"
            #img="props"
          >
            <v-img
              :key="image"
              :gradient="gradient"
              v-bind="props"
            />
          </template>
          <v-toolbar
            color="teal"
            dark
          >
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>

          </v-toolbar>

          <v-list>
            <v-list-group
              v-for="c in categories"
              :key="c.category_name"
              v-model="c.active"
              :prepend-icon="c.action"
              no-action
            >
              <template v-slot:activator>
                <v-list-item-content>
                  <v-list-item-title v-text="c.category_name"></v-list-item-title>
                </v-list-item-content>
              </template>

              <v-list-item
                v-for="n in c.notebooks"
                :key="n.notebook_name"
              >
                <v-list-item-content>
                  <v-list-item-title v-text="n.notebook_name"></v-list-item-title>
                </v-list-item-content>
              </v-list-item>
            </v-list-group>
          </v-list>
        </v-card>
      </v-col>

      <v-col
        cols="12"
        sm="6"
        md="8"
      >
        <ck></ck>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
  import ck from './CKEditor'

  export default {
    name: 'tc',
    data: () => ({
      categories: [
        {
          action: 'mdi-arrow-down-drop-circle-outline',
          active: true,
          notebooks: [{ notebook_name: '默认笔记' }],
          category_name: '默认笔记本',
        },
        {
          action: 'mdi-arrow-down-drop-circle-outline',
          notebooks: [
            { notebook_name: '百年孤独' },
            { notebook_name: '三体' },
            { notebook_name: '山海经' },
          ],
          category_name: '语文笔记本',
        },
        {
          action: 'mdi-arrow-down-drop-circle-outline',
          notebooks: [{ notebook_name: '数据链路层' }],
          category_name: '计算机网络',
        },
        {
          action: 'mdi-tag',
          notebooks: [{ notebook_name: '标签一' }],
          category_name: '便签笔记本',
        },
      ],
    }),
    components: {
      ck,
    },
  }
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
